   commenced in October 2018, upon the date we took possession of the
   leased space and committed to make $99.5 million in minimum fixed
   payments over the term of the lease agreement, although cash payments
   for rental obligations under the lease do not begin until October 2019.
   This lease contains a renewal option for two additional five-year
   periods and includes a tenant improvement allowance of $3.0 million.

