   for space to be used as our new corporate headquarters in New York
   City. This lease is expected to commence in August 2019 when we take
   possession of the leased space and commit to pay $503.0 million in
   minimum fixed payments over the term of the lease. This lease contains
   a renewal option for an additional 10-year period and includes a tenant
   improvement allowance of $28.0 million.


