   market practice of similar positions or internal pay equity when
   compared to the compensation paid to employees in similar positions who
   were not related to the Chairman of our board of directors and Chief
   Executive Officer. Ms. Foley was also eligible for equity awards on the
   same general terms and conditions as applicable to employees in similar
   positions who were not related to the Chairman of our board of
   directors and Chief Executive Officer.

