   agreement for a New York office and retail space at 5 Manhattan West
   (the 5 Manhattan West Lease). The 5 Manhattan West Lease commenced in
   October 2018, upon the date the Company took possession of the leased
   space and the Company is committed to $99.5 million in minimum fixed
   payments over the term of the lease although cash payments for rental
