   2018 was primarily due to an increase in net change in operating assets
   and liabilities of $81.5 million and non-cash adjustments of
   $16.1 million, partially offset by a net loss of $47.9 million. The
   increase in net change in operating assets and liabilities was
   primarily due to a $63.0 million increase in deferred revenue
